6:
Thank you for attending my concert.
It was a pleasure to play for you.
10:
That brings us to the end of today's
performance! Hope to see you at
the next one!
15: And thank you all for coming as well.
19:
Not at all. I'm glad we finally got to
hear you perform again.
24:
All of your concerts have been
selling out so quickly.
29:
She's a rising star all over the place
these days, not just in Palpebra!
33:
Lyra's fans—er, rather, the entire
guild mobilized to set up the concert
this time!
38:
I'm deeply grateful for the warm
reception I've received...
41:
But... I feel strange, somehow. This is
so much more than I could have
asked for, but I still feel like I haven't
done enough.
45:
I must play more. I need to reach
more hearts with my music...
55:
As a matter of fact...
I've got a special offer that might
help you accomplish just that!
62:
Wh-what do you think? It's not too...
garish or anything, right?
66: Not at all. It looks great on you!
72:
It's adorable. Beautiful. The very
pinnacle of cuteness.
77:
Is this for that upcoming Halloween
concert you and Lilie spoke of?
82:
Y-yes, that's right... She's the one
who gave it to me.
85:
I'm honored to be able to play, but...
Is it really okay for me to wear this?
90:
Sure it is. Dressing up's a big part of
Halloween, right?
94:
In that case, should I... do something
special with Carol as well?
103:
Oh, yes... As long as it didn't get in
the way of the strings, that would be
lovely—
106:
I was so busy paying off my debt, I
hadn't any time to consider such
things as festivals.
110:
But now, I... I know what it means to
have fun.
113:
And that's why I have to enjoy
myself this Halloween!
116:
I learned a single spell for
Halloween... "Trick or treat," I believe?
121:
"Spell" isn't quite right... More of a
festive phrase?
125:
Is that so? I was informed that those
words could charm others into
giving you candy...
134:
We're looking forward to your
concert, you know!
146:
Hello, everyone. Are you on your way
back from the Kaleidoscope?
150:
Yup. Are you getting ready for your
concert?
175:
This... isn't a normal part of the
festivities, is it?
179:
No, but... I guess it doesn't feel out of
place?
185: Are they here to play again?
190:
Hmph... They seem less dangerous
than last year, but...
201:
It looks like we can't simply let them
be. We've got to calm them down
somehow!
206:
...Perhaps I can help. Here goes
nothing!
217: Well... Did you all enjoy the show?
221:
That song just now... Why did they
vanish?
225:
I had the feeling they were simply in
the mood for some music.
238:
Thank you for saving us! Great
music, too!
240:
Here, have some candy from the
festival. It's the least I can do to
thank you!
247:
You can think of it as an early
Halloween haul.
